                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 25.369,
                                "byte_start": 100557,
                                "byte_stop": 202121,
                                "text": "The judgments and opinion of the Court in 75-746, Atlas Roofing against Occupational Safety and Health Review Board and the related case of 75-748, along with an unrelated case 75-1753 Santa Fe Industries against Green will each be announced by Mr. Justice White."
                            }
